Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. One Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where is my red cherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not a Manhattan without a cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you should pay more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Business is better when I have this in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll be jinxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.60,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(342,0)\pos(328,311)}Verden (Germany) \N Springer Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:10.44,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,149)\pos(315,306)}A Past Erased
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let there be some valuables left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was left intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they must have been loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's see if there is anything \N worthy of the great Heckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life sure is transient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a candidate for state governor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it is totally meaningless if you get shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, back to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their safe should be somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is with this cold feeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had this bad a feeling in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone in this room...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I getting all scared for?  That's not like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, he was behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst case scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All because that bartender forgot my red cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey officer, can't you cut me some slack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not taken anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You are in the same business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you put that dangerous looking \N thing down and talk this over peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be worse than the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw ups like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only pull the rest of us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, today sure is an unlucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you looked familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you that doctor from the newspaper who is an \N important witness to assemblyman Springer's murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I don't do unnecessary \N things like killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about the incident \N that took place in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you were some super \N first class surgeon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had an idea with my brilliant brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think people meet by chance, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are predestined to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I were destined to become partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of people who need someone \N like you in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying people who want to call for a doctor, \N but can't, because it is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave all the management to the great Heckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn you into the world's finest underworld doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can earn much more in the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be a millionaire in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going, Doctor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I have to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know about the murder in that mansion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did see the killer with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the killer a blond male of about twenty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me about the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only tell you if you team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the third floor of this tenement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I researched that assemblyman's mansion \N for a month after I laid eyes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I decided to make my move, he showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked through a window, I saw their dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could make some money if I shook \N him up a bit, so I followed the killer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your innocence in this case has now been proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go explain it all to the police or do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's talk about our wonderful future \N somewhere else over a drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good would it do to see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what the hell is he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someone like him, who I can make \N money off of, is hard to come by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not crossing dangerous bridges \N is one of my principles, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!  Are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot!  He's holding a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.. used to take walks with my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...down the road by a sunflower field...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on summer days like today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used that gun because someone asked you to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He spoke to me one day at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blond youth, about twenty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Erich had a beautiful smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called himself Erich this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We became friends after meeting several times...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he invited me to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To assemblyman Springer's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was living in that house until recently...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he said they loved him like a son for about a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I watched that house for about a month, \N but I didn't see anybody like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were a wonderful family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a photo of me and the assemblyman's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just could not forgive them for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sunflower garden on their property...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they tore it down to make room for parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said that was too cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Erich agreed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me you killed them just because of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Erich told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the assemblyman had a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he had stopped being the son of the assemblyman Springer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he wasn't a member of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to do him a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to eliminate that family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having an affair is such a horrible thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother... was also another man's lover...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving that aside, you wouldn't happen \N to know where their safe is, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was in the study on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry and get out of here too, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can erase the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can erase everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can reset your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can forget, you can't erase the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I thought of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I think I could erase my \N past if I pulled the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did I agree to his request?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Dr. Tenma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at his message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left you a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is in the study of that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew you would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erich said it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That your fate has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I told you to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good is dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is over if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stay alive, right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say something good every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are tracking down this dangerous \N serial killer named Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you forget about something \N that absurd and partner up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, when I tried to get into \N this room earlier, I felt a sudden chill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you shaking, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The monster inside me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...has grown this big, Dr. Tenma!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... enjoying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've arranged something good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you would team up with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was going to team up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you need money to run away from the police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is gonna take you to the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be keeping your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it back, do some work, get the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then come to Frank's on Graschten Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and make some big bucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is a profitable business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, since they paid me in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...guess I'll go have myself a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lawyer," I brought you a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry... and stop the bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An artery in your armpit has been damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this done with a shotgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the doctor is empty handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the surgical equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city is dangerous, so I didn't go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did have the equipment, I can't operate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have a real doctor take a look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would have done that already if we could!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long ago was he shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask stupid questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four hours ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the terrorists from this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of treating someone \N who commits mindless terrorism!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the position you are in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other group members will be coming to help us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, please stop the bleeding at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... Lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, my life is in this doctor's hands right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, you can shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not running a charity here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you return the 25,000 Marks you owe us, Heckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I do want to return the money I owe you, Mr. Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that feeling alone makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, break both of his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay!  I'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please wait another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:18.04,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the terrorists who used small, automatic \N weapons this morning at Erfurt Station...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break both of his legs too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.96,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...based on the testimony of a witness, \N the suspects have been identified as...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.67,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...Max Steindorf and Karl Brandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:26.84,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,The GWE...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.46,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...has announced that they will pay anyone \N who provides crucial information...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.42,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...300,000 Marks as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can pay back the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I know where they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can forget about the debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you are not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll snap your neck if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!  It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but Tenma is there right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was mindless terrorism, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did definitely has meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...feel so good that I killed that bastard \N president of the GWE...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...t-that I don't care if die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a lawyer in East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was the secretary of a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody had a job once the wall came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, do you know how we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That GWE company...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right after the wall came down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...invaded the east by letting their money do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They forcefully built factories... on our land...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless number of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was our country...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot that bastard with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot him... with pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others should be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared of dying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone died like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All twelve of the people you killed died just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what it means to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me disinfectant and scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You at least have that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An arterial hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is going into shock caused by low blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stopping the bleeding by applying pressure \N to the severed arteries with my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to suture the wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me a needle and some string!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't you have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a stapler will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stapler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given him first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm carrying him to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't put him down, I'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are going to shoot me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then you will have to carry this man to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I saw your face somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are that doctor who is suspected \N of serial murders, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was not mindless terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the president of the GWE...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...his lackeys, and their bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are saying that nobody got caught in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... that child in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew that you shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save a guy like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not because you were afraid you would be shot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are not those of someone \N who is afraid of being shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did you save a killer like myself \N who commits random terrorism...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I believe that you are human...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an excellent doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened to the money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you just treated him and came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:11.76,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorists responsible for the attack \N on Erfurt Station have been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you say something ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.97,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,The police had the hideout surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.98,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...but unexpectedly, the terrorists showed no signs of resistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.81,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...and quietly turned themselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not running a charity here, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
